@RepStefanik The fentanyl is not coming from Mexico. It's manufactured in China and the USA. Everyone knows this except your ill-informed constituents. 

Janssen Pharmaceutica first developed fentanyl in 1959
Janssen Pharmaceutica is owned by Johnson and Johnson, which is a global company.

@POTUS The government must spend less. 

Entitlements are much larger than military spending. So, that is the main starting point.

But, don't get me wrong, I am all for reduction in military spending considering how peaceful Russia, China, Iran and N Korea are.
